\begin{question}
Given the function shown below, evaluate the following:
\begin{enumerate}[(a)]
\item $\displaystyle \lim_{x \rightarrow -2} f(x)$
\item $\displaystyle \lim_{x \rightarrow 0}f(x)$
\item $\displaystyle \lim_{x \rightarrow 2}f(x)$
\end{enumerate}
